#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The Journey from 0.3 to 1.0"
msgstr "El viaje de 0,3 a 1,0"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The 0.3.x series was our first production-quality SDK, supporting JSON-RPC, gRPC, REST transports, security with OAuth2/Keycloak, and cloud-native deployment with persistent stores and replicated queues. The 1.0 series modernized the SDK to align with the final A2A Specification 1.0.0."
msgstr "La serie 0.3.x fue nuestro primer SDK con calidad de producción, compatible con JSON-RPC, gRPC, transportes REST, seguridad con OAuth2/Keycloak y despliegue nativo en la nube con almacenes persistentes y colas replicadas. La serie 1.0 modernizó el SDK para alinearlo con la especificación final A2A 1.0.0."

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Here is a summary of the major changes. Each of our previous blog posts covers its respective release in detail:"
msgstr "He aquí un resumen de los principales cambios. Cada una de nuestras entradas de blog anteriores cubre su respectiva versión en detalle:"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Specification and API"
msgstr "Especificación y API"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*A2A Protocol 1.0 alignment* -- the SDK implements the final https://a2a-protocol.org/v1.0.0/specification/[A2A Specification 1.0.0], including the new `supportedInterfaces` model for `AgentCard`, removal of `kind` discriminators, and refined error handling (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1])"
msgstr "*Alineación del Protocolo A2A 1.0* - el SDK implementa la link:https://a2a-protocol.org/v1.0.0/specification/[Especificación A2A 1.0.0] final, incluido el nuevo modelo `supportedInterfaces` para `AgentCard` , la eliminación de los discriminadores `kind` y un tratamiento de errores perfeccionado ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Java records throughout* -- all spec domain classes are now Java records, providing immutability, consistent accessor naming (`card.name()` instead of `card.getName()`), and less boilerplate (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1])"
msgstr "Registros *Java en todas partes* - todas las clases del dominio spec son ahora registros Java, lo que proporciona inmutabilidad, una nomenclatura coherente de los accesores ( `card.name()` en lugar de `card.getName()` ), y menos boilerplate ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*AgentEmitter API* -- replaced the `EventQueue` + `TaskUpdater` combination with a streamlined `AgentEmitter` interface for agent interactions (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[Alpha2])"
msgstr "*AgentEmitter API* - sustituye la combinación `EventQueue` + `TaskUpdater` por una interfaz `AgentEmitter` simplificada para las interacciones con los agentes ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[Alpha2] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Structured error codes* -- A2A error types now carry structured codes and details for precise error handling (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released/[Beta1])"
msgstr "*Códigos de error estructurados* - Los tipos de error A2A llevan ahora códigos y detalles estructurados para una gestión precisa de los errores ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released/[Beta1] )"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Server Architecture"
msgstr "Arquitectura de servidores"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*MainEventBus architecture* -- the server internals were rearchitected around a central event bus. Previously, event processing was driven directly by client requests. Now all events flow through a single-threaded `MainEventBusProcessor` that persists events to the `TaskStore` _before_ distributing them to clients. This guarantees clients never see unpersisted events, eliminates race conditions in concurrent task updates, and enables patterns like fire-and-forget tasks and late client reconnections (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[Alpha2])"
msgstr "*Arquitectura MainEventBus* - las partes internas del servidor se han rediseñado en torno a un bus de eventos central. Anteriormente, el procesamiento de eventos era dirigido directamente por las peticiones de los clientes. Ahora todos los eventos fluyen a través de un único hilo `MainEventBusProcessor` que persiste los eventos en `TaskStore` _antes de_ distribuirlos a los clientes. Esto garantiza que los clientes nunca vean eventos no persistidos, elimina las condiciones de carrera en las actualizaciones de tareas concurrentes y permite patrones como las tareas \"disparar y olvidar\" y las reconexiones tardías de clientes ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[Alpha2] )"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Infrastructure"
msgstr "Infraestructura"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*New coordinates* -- Maven `groupId` changed to `org.a2aproject.sdk` and Java packages renamed to `org.a2aproject.sdk.*`, reflecting the project's home under the https://github.com/a2aproject[A2A Project organization] (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released/[Beta1])"
msgstr "*Nuevas coordenadas* - Maven `groupId` cambiado a `org.a2aproject.sdk` y los paquetes Java renombrados a `org.a2aproject.sdk.*` , reflejando el hogar del proyecto bajo la link:https://github.com/a2aproject[organización del Proyecto A2A] ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-beta1-released/[Beta1] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Protobuf as source of truth* -- replaced Jackson with Gson and established `a2a.proto` as the authoritative definition, with MapStruct mappers giving compile errors if spec and proto diverge (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1])"
msgstr "*Protobuf como fuente de la verdad* - sustituyó a Jackson por Gson y estableció `a2a.proto` como la definición autorizada, con mappers MapStruct dando errores de compilación si spec y proto divergen ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Maven BOMs* -- three BOMs (`a2a-java-sdk-bom`, `a2a-java-extras-bom`, `a2a-java-reference-bom`) for dependency management (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1])"
msgstr "*Maven BOMs* - tres BOMs ( `a2a-java-sdk-bom` , `a2a-java-extras-bom` , `a2a-java-reference-bom` ) para la gestión de dependencias ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha1/[Alpha1] )"

#. type: Title ==
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Capabilities"
msgstr "Capacidades"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*OpenTelemetry telemetry* -- built-in tracing and monitoring for both client and server (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[1.0.0.Alpha2])"
msgstr "*Telemetría OpenTelemetry* - rastreo y monitorización incorporados tanto para el cliente como para el servidor ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[1.0.0.Alpha2] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Push notifications* -- full server and client support per the A2A 1.0 spec (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[1.0.0.Alpha2])"
msgstr "*Notificaciones push* - soporte completo de servidor y cliente según la especificación A2A 1.0 ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-alpha2-released/[1.0.0.Alpha2] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*v0.3 backward compatibility* -- a compatibility layer that lets v1.0 agents interoperate with v0.3 agents and clients across all three transports, with multi-version convenience modules for serving both protocol versions simultaneously (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1])"
msgstr "*Compatibilidad con versiones anteriores v0.3* : una capa de compatibilidad que permite a los agentes v1.0 interoperar con agentes y clientes v0.3 en los tres transportes, con módulos de conveniencia multiversión para servir simultáneamente ambas versiones del protocolo ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Android HTTP client* -- `AndroidA2AHttpClient` using `HttpURLConnection` makes the SDK usable on Android (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1])"
msgstr "*Cliente HTTP Android* - `AndroidA2AHttpClient` usando `HttpURLConnection` hace que el SDK sea utilizable en Android ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1] )"

#. type: Plain text
#: _posts/2026-06-10-a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-final-released.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Spec-compliant SSE parser* -- a robust `ServerSentEvent` record with full SSE spec compliance (https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1])"
msgstr "*Analizador sintáctico SSE conforme a* las especificaciones: un registro `ServerSentEvent` robusto y totalmente conforme a las especificaciones SSE ( link:https://quarkus.io/blog/a2a-java-sdk-1-0-0-cr1-released/[1.0.0.CR1] )"

